            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>acrum</ex></expan></supplied> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> Antinoe et Phoebe <lb n="2"/>duae sunt conservae <lb n="3"/>sorores servae Vo<lb break="no" n="4"/>lusiorum Marci et Aemiliani <lb n="5"/>hic sunt positae Phoebe vixit <lb n="6"/>annis VI <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>ensibus</ex></expan> X <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iebus</ex></expan> XV Antinoe <lb n="7"/>annum <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>ies</ex></expan> XX P<expan><ex>h</ex><abbr>oebus</abbr></expan> et Rhodope <lb n="8"/>filiabus pientissimis et Tertius <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuerunt</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Die Fundumstände der Stele sind unbekannt. (A): falsche B-Höhe. Inschrift teilweise metrisch.</p>
